quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,Ngifunga ngalokho okugijimayo (amahashi) okukhefuzelayo
  100,2,Okukhipha umlilo
  100,3,Amahashi ahlasela ekuseni
  100,4,Futhi ngifunga ngamahashi avusa uthuli
  100,5,Kanye nokufika lapho maphakathi beyisixuku
  100,6,Ngempela umuntu eNkosini yakhe akabongi
  100,7,Futhi ngempela yena kulokho ungufakazi
  100,8,Futhi ngempela yena usothandweni kakhulu lengcebo
  100,9,Ngakube akazi yini ukuthi ngenkathi kusakazwa lokho okusemangcwabeni
  100,10,Futhi kwenziwa kwaziwa lokho okusezifubeni
  100,11,Ngempela iNkosi yabo ngalolosuku (lokwahlulela) iyazi kabanzi ngabo